POLICE are investigating an assault on a 27-year-old man in Glasgow. Police probe assault on man in Glasgow POLICE are investigating an assault on a 27-year-old man in Glasgow.He was taken to Glasgow Royal Infirmary with serious injuries after being attacked on St George's Road at around 5.50pm on Thursday.The man is in a stable condition and the scene of the attack has been cordoned off while police probe the circumstances. 